Dastakein Aftermovie [10 city tour] 🚪 

So much has happened over the last few months, so many ups and downs. I’ve stood in front of thousands of people and poured my heart out. With this movie we’ve tried to capture two extraordinary months in two beautiful minutes. Enjoy x 
Thank you for everything. 🤍

latestPosts.caption:
‘Afsos’ w @apdhillon 🥀 Song out on 31/01 x

BTS / met AP and Shinda in Delhi and played them the verses that I had already written for the song. And they both loved the parts. Post that we locked the structure in about 10 mins and these guys just took 2 hours to write the most beautiful lines for AP’s part. Crazy how we got my reaction on camera right after they played me their bit x
